---
import { whatsappUrl } from '../../data/landing';
---

<header id="home" class="relative overflow-hidden pt-28 sm:pt-32">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_top,rgba(14,165,233,0.12),transparent_30%),linear-gradient(180deg,#050816_0%,#080f1f_55%,#0f172a_100%)]"></div>
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('/fondo-hero.webp')] bg-cover bg-center opacity-22 mix-blend-screen"></div>
  <div
    class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 opacity-60"
    style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(148,163,184,0.06) 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(148,163,184,0.06) 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 72px 72px; mask-image: radial-gradient(circle at center, black, transparent 82%);"
  ></div>
  <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.08] mix-blend-screen" style="background-image: radial-gradient(circle at 1px 1px, rgba(255,255,255,0.8) 1px, transparent 0); background-size: 26px 26px;"></div>
  <div class="pointer-events-none absolute -left-24 top-24 h-72 w-72 rounded-full bg-cyan-400/10 blur-3xl animate-float-slow"></div>
  <div class="pointer-events-none absolute -right-20 top-40 h-80 w-80 rounded-full bg-blue-500/10 blur-3xl animate-float"></div>
  <div class="pointer-events-none absolute left-1/2 top-16 h-168 w-2xl -translate-x-1/2 rounded-full bg-cyan-300/10 blur-[180px] animate-pulse-glow"></div>

  <section
    id="hero-spotlight"
    style="--x: 50%; --y: 30%; background-image: radial-gradient(circle at var(--x) var(--y), rgba(56,189,248,0.25), transparent 280px), radial-gradient(circle at 20% 20%, rgba(59,130,246,0.15), transparent 36%), linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(5,8,22,0.92), rgba(8,15,31,0.98));"
    class="relative mx-auto max-w-7xl overflow-hidden px-4 pb-24 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"
  >
    <div
      class="absolute inset-0 border border-white/5"
      style="background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); backdrop-filter: blur(2px);"
    ></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 animate-shimmer bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_top_left,rgba(34,211,238,0.08),transparent_25%),radial-gradient(circle_at_bottom_right,rgba(16,185,129,0.05),transparent_30%)]"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-x-0 top-0 h-28 bg-linear-to-b from-[#050816] via-transparent to-transparent"></div>

    <div class="relative grid items-center gap-14 lg:grid-cols-[1.15fr_0.85fr] lg:gap-10">
      <div class="space-y-8 py-12 sm:py-16 lg:py-20" data-reveal>
        <div class="premium-chip inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full px-4 py-2 text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-cyan-100/90 animate-pulse-glow" data-reveal style="--reveal-delay: 80ms;">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-bolt text-cyan-300"></i>
          Diseño premium para negocios locales
        </div>

        <div class="max-w-4xl space-y-6" data-reveal style="--reveal-delay: 140ms;">
          <h1 class="text-balance text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-5xl lg:text-7xl" style="text-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(34,211,238,0.08);">
            Páginas web modernas para negocios que quieren vender más
          </h1>
          <p class="max-w-2xl text-base leading-8 text-slate-300 sm:text-lg">
            Creo sitios elegantes, rápidos y enfocados en conversión para negocios pequeños y medianos que necesitan verse profesionales, destacar en su zona y convertir visitas en clientes.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 sm:flex-row" data-reveal style="--reveal-delay: 220ms;">
          <a href={whatsappUrl} class="premium-button inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-3 rounded-full px-6 py-3.5 text-sm font-semibold animate-pulse-glow">
            <i class="fa-brands fa-whatsapp text-lg"></i>
            Cotizar por WhatsApp
          </a>
          <a href="#proyectos" class="premium-button-secondary inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-3 rounded-full px-6 py-3.5 text-sm font-semibold">
            Ver proyectos
            <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right text-xs text-cyan-200"></i>
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="grid gap-3 sm:grid-cols-3" data-reveal style="--reveal-delay: 300ms;">
          <div class="premium-surface rounded-2xl bg-[linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(255,255,255,0.08),rgba(255,255,255,0.03))] p-4">
            <p class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white">+Rápida</p>
            <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-300">Carga ligera y experiencia fluida.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="premium-surface rounded-2xl bg-[linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(255,255,255,0.08),rgba(255,255,255,0.03))] p-4">
            <p class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white">Responsive</p>
            <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-300">Se adapta perfecto a celular.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="premium-surface rounded-2xl bg-[linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(255,255,255,0.08),rgba(255,255,255,0.03))] p-4">
            <p class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white">Conversión</p>
            <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-300">Pensada para generar cotizaciones.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="relative mx-auto w-full max-w-xl" data-reveal style="--reveal-delay: 180ms;">
        <div class="absolute inset-8 blur-3xl animate-pulse-glow" style="border-radius: 2rem; background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(34,211,238,0.24), transparent 62%);"></div>
        <div class="premium-surface relative rounded-[2rem] bg-[linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(255,255,255,0.08),rgba(255,255,255,0.03))] p-5 sm:p-6">
          <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 bg-[linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(255,255,255,0.08),transparent_28%,transparent_72%,rgba(255,255,255,0.05))] opacity-70"></div>
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between border-b border-white/10 pb-4">
            <div>
              <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-cyan-200/70">Presencia digital</p>
              <p class="mt-2 text-xl font-semibold text-white">Marco Webs Studio</p>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-full border border-cyan-300/20 bg-cyan-300/10 px-3 py-1 text-xs text-cyan-100 shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(34,211,238,0.16)]">Disponible</div>
          </div>

          <div class="grid gap-4 py-5 sm:grid-cols-2">
            <div class="premium-surface rounded-2xl bg-[#050816]/60 p-4" data-reveal style="--reveal-delay: 120ms;">
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-300">Web profesional</p>
              <p class="mt-3 text-3xl font-semibold text-white">Diseño + estrategia</p>
              <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-400">Contenido claro, visual premium y llamadas a la acción.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="premium-surface rounded-2xl bg-[#050816]/60 p-4" data-reveal style="--reveal-delay: 180ms;">
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-300">WhatsApp listo</p>
              <p class="mt-3 text-3xl font-semibold text-white">Cotizaciones</p>
              <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-400">Conexión directa para cerrar prospectos sin fricción.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="grid gap-3 border-t border-white/10 pt-5 text-sm text-slate-300 sm:grid-cols-3">
            <div class="premium-tag rounded-2xl p-3" data-reveal style="--reveal-delay: 220ms;">Negocios locales</div>
            <div class="premium-tag rounded-2xl p-3" data-reveal style="--reveal-delay: 280ms;">Branding moderno</div>
            <div class="premium-tag rounded-2xl p-3" data-reveal style="--reveal-delay: 340ms;">Resultados reales</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <script>
    const hero = document.querySelector<HTMLElement>('#hero-spotlight');

    if (hero) {
      const updateSpotlight = (event: MouseEvent) => {
        const bounds = hero.getBoundingClientRect();
        hero.style.setProperty('--x', `${event.clientX - bounds.left}px`);
        hero.style.setProperty('--y', `${event.clientY - bounds.top}px`);
      };

      const handleMouseLeave = () => {
        hero.style.setProperty('--x', '50%');
        hero.style.setProperty('--y', '30%');
      };

      hero.addEventListener('mousemove', updateSpotlight);
      hero.addEventListener('mouseleave', handleMouseLeave);
    }
  </script>
